{"ts":"2026-07-06T08:03:06.673Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/444\n\n## Problem\nMutations fall back to author \"unknown\" when PM_AUTHOR is unset and author_default is empty (the init default). Stateless CLI agents get a fresh env per shell call, so attribution silently degrades to \"unknown\" — breaking history/claims/comments provenance that multi-agent coordination depends on.\n\n## Proposed fix\n(1) top-level global `--author <id>` flag; (2) `pm init` records a stable author_default (prompt or derive from git config/hostname); (3) pm health/validate warning when recent mutations carry author \"unknown\" with fix-hint `pm config set author-default <id>`.\n\n## Definition of done\nGlobal --author works on all mutations; init writes a non-empty author_default; unknown-author advisory ships with remediation-registry entry; docs/AGENTS.md updated. Related: GH-458 item covers the claim-time --assignee alias."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-cpja"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-444: ergonomic author attribution — global --author, init author_default, unknown-author advisory"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood GH-444: stateless CLI agents lose PM_AUTHOR between shell calls and mutations degrade to author 'unknown', breaking provenance. Duplicate check: searched author attribution/unknown fallback — only closed dedup refactor pm-xh0y; no open overlap."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:cli","gh-issue","multi-agent"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:06.673Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:06.673Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":150},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Global --author flag works on all mutations; pm init records non-empty author_default; health/validate advisory flags recent author:unknown mutations with fix-hint; docs updated"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"ea5bf6b355504c4f7e3c27f63dcd6f7e14562682deb779bcd40f73d0b214cc62","message":""}
